* Jōgan 6 (864): Honke moved from Harima Province to Kawachi Province
* Undated: {{ill|Senior Seventh Rank|ja|正七位上|1=Senior Seventh Rank|lt=Senior Seventh Rank, Upper Grade|12=draft}}, Onmyō Assistant
* Jōgan 15 (873): Honke moved to Ukyo Sanjō Second Ward
* Undated: {{ill|Senior Sixth Rank|ja|正六位上|1=Senior Sixth Rank|lt=Senior Sixth Rank, Upper Grade|12=draft}}, Onmyō Subordinate
* Jōgan 19 (877): Promoted to {{ill|Junior Fifth Rank|ja|従五位下|1=Junior Fifth Rank|lt=Junior Fifth Rank, Lower Grade|12=draft}} (Outer). Clan name changed to Sukune
* Undated: Assistant in Bizen Province
* Genkei 6 (882): Promoted to Junior Fifth Rank (Inner)
* Ninna 1 (885): Appointed Chief of the Bureau of Onmyō
* Engi 8 (908): Passed away<ref name="skf" />

